ZH: 我们无法掌控命运的走向。
EN: We cannot control the course of destiny.

ZH: 她认为命运注定了他们的相遇。
EN: She believed that fate destined their encounter.

ZH: 命运曲折，但可以被改变。
EN: Destiny may be full of twists and turns, but it can be altered.

ZH: 我们每个人都有自己的命运。
EN: Each one of us has our own destiny.

ZH: 命运将他们带到了一起。
EN: Destiny brought them together.

ZH: 他们相信人应该顺应命运。
EN: They believed that people should follow their destiny.

ZH: 命运往往是不可预测的。
EN: Destiny is often unpredictable.

ZH: 命运之轮不停地转动。
EN: The wheel of destiny keeps turning.

ZH: 命运是无法逃避的。
EN: Destiny is unavoidable.

ZH: 我们必须接受自己的命运。
EN: We must accept our own destiny.

ZH: 命运创造了一个机会给他们。
EN: Destiny created an opportunity for them.

ZH: 他们的命运紧密相连。
EN: Their destinies are closely intertwined.

ZH: 命运之手安排一切。
EN: The hand of destiny orchestrates everything.

