EN: Destiny made them meet at the same time.

ZH: 命运有时候是残酷的。
EN: Destiny can be cruel at times.

ZH: 命运把他们的生活彻底改变了。
EN: Destiny completely changed their lives.

ZH: 命运让他们变得更强大。
